April 2020: While whole world is locked down because of spread of Corona virus, I'm listening to this beautiful song. 
In this part of the world, Government has banned high speed internet even in such difficult times when internet is only mode of interaction and entertainment. The song is playing, stopping, buffering, playing... 
We shall overcome!
